#LetsGameItOut #OperaGX

I Broke Everything in This Entire City - Vending Machine Business Simulator - Let's Game It Out

----------

Check it out on Steam ‚ñ∫ https://store.steampowered.com/app/2998750/Vending_Machine_Business_Simulator/

More about Vending Machine Business Simulator (from Steam):

Vending Machine Business Simulator is a simulation game where you start with very little money in your pocket and build a vending empire that spreads across the city. Work for others and once you have the necessary experience and money, start your own business.

Manage Your Machines:
Purchase, place, and maintain vending machines across different locations. Keep track of inventory and ensure machines are stocked and operational.

Optimize Profits:
Follow local events, adjust pricing strategies, and optimize product offerings to maximize revenue and profitability.

Expand Your Empire:
Unlock new locations and unlock new type of machines to attract more customers and increase sales.

Dynamic Challenges:
Overcome challenges such as machine malfunctions, aggressive customers, changing consumer trends, and economic changes.

Realistic Simulation:
Experience a realistic simulation of the vending machine business, including factors like machine maintenance, customer preferences.

Are you ready to embark on the journey to vending success?

snippet.title: Busting Scary Mario Myths to Prove them Real!
snippet.description:
There‚Äôs so many Terrifying myths in the Mario series. For example Myth: The Creepy Mario 64 piano won‚Äôt notice you if you're crawling. And we're testing the scariest Mario myths to see if they're true or false. Starting off with simple, like the ghostly galaxy mansion doesn't load in properly when you look back at it. And the myths will get more sinister as we go on.

Are you brave enough to uncover the darkest secrets of the Mushroom Kingdom? In this spine-chilling video, we delve into Creepy Mario Myths That Will Keep You Up at Night‚Äîmysteries so eerie they‚Äôll make you think twice about your favorite childhood games. From hidden horrors in iconic levels to rumors of ghostly encounters and unexplained phenomena, these legends blur the line between fact and fiction.

The haunting story behind the Killer Piano in Big Boo's Haunt‚Äîand the chilling sound that comes with it
The unsettling mystery of Luigi‚Äôs Shadow in Super Mario 64‚Äîcould it be a ghostly Easter egg or something more sinister?
Dark whispers and distorted music in the ‚ÄúUnfinished Levels‚Äù of Mario games 
The creepy origins of Wario‚Äôs face on the cover of Mario 64 DS 
Why some players believe Bowser‚Äôs laugh hides a terrifying secret 
And much more that will leave you questioning the innocence of the Mushroom Kingdom.

These myths aren‚Äôt just eerie tales‚Äîthey‚Äôre backed by stories from players who swear they‚Äôve experienced these chilling events firsthand. Could there be some truth to these rumors, or are they just creative fabrications from overactive imaginations?

This is the side of Mario you‚Äôve never seen before‚Äîthe side that might haunt your dreams. Don‚Äôt watch alone in the dark!

A natural talent, Quando Rondo was once a small child, secretly singing in the bathroom as a 9-year-old boy in Savannah, GA. His natural gravitation towards music lead to him to hip-hop; he began recording his fledgling verses on his cell phone. He quickly gained traction online, racking up millions of views on YouTube.

Fittingly, he titled his 2018 mixtape 'Life B4 Fame' with the hopes that things would change for the better once his career really took off. He was right‚Äîwithin two days, his mixtape had amassed more than one million streams on MyMixtapez. Things will only go up from there, and if the snippets from his forthcoming Rich Homie Quando project are any sign, he‚Äôs only only getting better with time.

#QuandoRondo #Hereforareason #GrowUp

snippet.title: Venezuela 1 - 1 Brasil  | Eliminatorias Sudamericanas al Mundial 2026 | Fecha 11
snippet.description:
Brasil parece no poder encontrar su rumbo y, despu√©s de haber logrado dos victorias en la √∫ltima doble fecha, se tuvo que contentar con un empate por 1-1 ante Venezuela, en el marco de las Eliminatorias Sudamericanas.

Desde el inicio, el Scratch parec√≠a m√°s decidido a romper el cero en el marcador. As√≠, la acumulaci√≥n de chances en favor del equipo de Dorival Junior se hac√≠a presente, incluso con un remate en el palo de Vinicius que, tras el rebote, Gerson no pudo enviar al fondo de la red.

Venezuela resist√≠a, pero los errores desde el fondo en Brasil le presentaban oportunidades. Sin embargo, la falta de punter√≠a tambi√©n se hizo presente en la Vinotinto que, si no se encontraba con la humanidad de Ederson, tampoco le embocaba al arco. De todas maneras, el primer tiempo era de ida y vuelta y los 22 jugadores dentro del campo de juego entreten√≠an a los presentes.

La igualdad finalmente se romper√≠a sobre el final del primer tiempo, de la mano de un potente tiro libre de Raphinha a los 42 minutos que logr√≥ enga√±ar a Rafael Romo, quien no logr√≥ contener el remate a pesar de que el mismo fue hacia su palo. El v√©rtigo persisti√≥ en el segundo tiempo ya que, antes del minuto de juego, Telasco Segovia conect√≥ un lindo centro atr√°s de Jefferson Savarino para romperle el arco a Ederson y poner las cosas 1-1 en el marcador, para el delirio de los hinchas locales. La alegr√≠a, sin embargo, dur√≥ poco ya que, a los 13 minutos, una infracci√≥n sobre Vin√≠cius en el borde del √°rea fue sancionada con un penal -VAR mediante- para Brasil. De todas maneras, para fortuna del equipo del Bocha Batista, el delantero de Real Madrid malogr√≥ su intento desde los 12 pasos y tambi√©n en el rebote, luego de que Romo evite la ca√≠da de su valla.

La expulsi√≥n de Alexander Gonz√°lez sobre el final del partido amag√≥ con generar espacios para que Brasil encuentre la victoria, pero poco tiempo quedaba en el reloj para que el Scratch consiga el gol de la diferencia. As√≠, las cosas terminaron 1-1 en Matur√≠n, un empate que dej√≥ a Brasil en el tercer puesto de las Eliminatorias con 17 unidades, mientras que Venezuela se consolida, moment√°neamente, en el 7¬∞ puesto con 12 unidades, en zona de repechaje.

Ahora, el equipo de Batista vistar√° a Chile el pr√≥ximo 19 de noviembre para cerrar la doble fecha, mientras que los brasile√±os recibir√°n a Uruguay en el √∫ltimo partido de la jornada, el mismo d√≠a.

snippet.title: Tesla Model 3 Performance vs BMW M3 Competition ‚Äî Track Battle ‚Äî Cammisa's Ultimate Comparison Test
snippet.description:
Now with Endurance Mode, can the Highland Tesla M3P defeat the updated, reigning LCI BMW M3 Competition xDrive to become the new benchmark in sport sedans? This ultimate comparison test includes a Track Test Laptime Battle and an Endurance Race starring Randy Pobst.

The old-school comparison test is back!

===
Join the Hagerty Driver's Club: https://bit.ly/Join-HDC-Cammisa-ICONS
===
 
In this video, Hagerty's veteran automotive journalist Jason Cammisa answers the EV vs ICE question ‚Äî by taking an agnostic view that includes multiple different tests.

Chapters:
0:00 Introduction: EV vs ICE Holy War
3:13 2024 BMW M3: the Updated Benchmark
3:56 2024 "Highland" Model 3 Performance
4:31 Drifting Challenge: Model 3 vs M3
8:13 Will The Tesla's Brakes Overheat? Challenge Setup.
10:20 Randy Pobst Track Impressions, M3 and Model 3
11:44 Laptime Battle with Randy Pobst
13:14  Model 3 "Endurance Mode" 15-minute race
16:51 Laptime Analysis ‚Äî Overheating Tesla?
18:40  Everyday Driving Comparison
21:37  Backroad Driving Comparison
24:18  Purchase Price Difference
26:04  Winner: Tesla Model 3 Performance

On the way to reachin' my goals, lot of doors open and close (Open and close)
I've been spendin' millions on clothes, I been makin' millions off clothes (Millions off clothes)
Stackin' new money to old, garments they vintage and old (Vintage and old)
Cut up my shirt full of holes, GunWunna got a lot of hoes (Got a lot of hoes)
Shoutout my cousin, my cuz , my kin, my blood, my folk (My folk)
Hold my ten , I plant the seed, give it water to grow (For my team)
Half a million euros in a third-world country, I travel the coast (Travelin', yeah)
Always said that I wanted, young Wunna done done it, I do what they don't (Young Wunna, the man)

[Chorus]
They was tryna stunt my growth, I was steady chasin' my goals
Nigga, why you watchin'? I'm grown, nigga can't take my throne
Goin' through the motions, stay strong, he done been him all along (Him)

Freaky lil' bitch, she swallow my kids (She swallow my kids)

Marbella Spain ', and the view is the insane round the corner from Jordan (Jordan)
Speed in the coupe, Jeff Gordon, I got the foreign imported (Foreign imported)
Knew that we sold out the Barclay', now we gon' sell out the Garden (Gon' sell out the Garden)
Drop, I'ma fuck up the market, young Gunna really a martian (I'm really a martian)
Excusin' me through like a pardon, and I'm protected by carbons

[Chorus]
They was tryna stunt my growth, I was steady chasin' my goals
Nigga, why you watchin'? I'm grown, nigga can't take my throne
Goin' through the motions, stay strong, he done been him all along (Him)
Look at all this money we done grown, lot of different places I done flown

[Outro]
On the way to
 finish my goals, lot of doors open and close

Goin' through the motions, stay strong, he done been him all along

snippet.title: BEATLES ‚Äô64 - watch the new trailer.
snippet.description:
Journey back to 1964 and experience Beatlemania like never before. 

From producer Martin Scorsese and director David Tedeschi, stream Beatles '64, an original documentary, only on @disneyplus November 29.

The film captures the electrifying moment of The Beatles‚Äô first visit to America.¬† On February 7, 1964, The Beatles arrived in New York City to unprecedented excitement and hysteria. From the instant they landed at Kennedy Airport, met by thousands of fans, Beatlemania swept New York and the entire country. Their thrilling debut performance on The Ed Sullivan Show captivated more than 73 million viewers, the most watched television event of its time. Beatles ‚Äô64 presents the spectacle, but also tells a more intimate behind the scenes story, capturing the camaraderie of John, Paul, George, and Ringo as they experienced unimaginable fame.

The film includes rare footage filmed by pioneering documentarians Albert and David Maysles, beautifully restored in 4K by Park Road Post in New Zealand. The live performances from The Beatles‚Äô first American concert at the Washington, DC Coliseum and their Ed Sullivan appearances were demixed by WingNut Films and remixed by Giles Martin. Spotlighting this singular cultural moment and its continued resonance today, the music and footage are augmented by newly filmed interviews with Paul and Ringo, as well as fans whose lives were transformed by The Beatles.

Beatles ‚Äô64 is directed by David Tedeschi and produced by Martin Scorsese, Margaret Bodde, Paul McCartney, Ringo Starr, Olivia Harrison, Sean Ono Lennon, Jonathan Clyde, and Mikaela Beardsley, with Jeff Jones and Rick Yorn serving as executive producers.

@johnlennon @PaulMcCartney @GeorgeHarrisonOfficial @ringostarr

snippet.title: The Amateur | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the trailer for #TheAmateur starring Oscar¬Æ winner Rami Malek (‚ÄúBohemian Rhapsody‚Äù) and Academy Award¬Æ nominee Laurence Fishburne (‚ÄúWhat‚Äôs Love Got to Do with It‚Äù). The all-new espionage thriller opens in theaters nationwide April 11, 2025.

Charlie Heller (Malek) is a brilliant, but deeply introverted decoder for the CIA working out of a basement office at headquarters in Langley whose life is turned upside down when his wife is killed in a London terrorist attack. When his supervisors refuse to take action, he takes matters into his own hands, embarking on a dangerous trek across the globe to track down those responsible, his intelligence serving as the ultimate weapon for eluding his pursuers and achieving his revenge. The film also stars Rachel Brosnahan, Caitr√≠ona Balfe, Jon Bernthal, Michael Stuhlbarg, Holt McCallany, Julianne Nicholson, Adrian Martinez, Danny Sapani, and Laurence Fishburne. ‚ÄúThe Amateur‚Äù is directed by James Hawes. The screenplay is by Ken Nolan and Gary Spinelli based on the novel by Robert Littell. The film is produced by Hutch Parker, p.g.a., Dan Wilson, p.g.a., Rami Malek, Joel B. Michaels, with JJ Hook serving as executive producer.

localized.description:
Watch the trailer for #TheAmateur starring Oscar¬Æ winner Rami Malek (‚ÄúBohemian Rhapsody‚Äù) and Academy Award¬Æ nominee Laurence Fishburne (‚ÄúWhat‚Äôs Love Got to Do with It‚Äù). The all-new espionage thriller opens in theaters nationwide April 11, 2025.

Charlie Heller (Malek) is a brilliant, but deeply introverted decoder for the CIA working out of a basement office at headquarters in Langley whose life is turned upside down when his wife is killed in a London terrorist attack. When his supervisors refuse to take action, he takes matters into his own hands, embarking on a dangerous trek across the globe to track down those responsible, his intelligence serving as the ultimate weapon for eluding his pursuers and achieving his revenge. The film also stars Rachel Brosnahan, Caitr√≠ona Balfe, Jon Bernthal, Michael Stuhlbarg, Holt McCallany, Julianne Nicholson, Adrian Martinez, Danny Sapani, and Laurence Fishburne. ‚ÄúThe Amateur‚Äù is directed by James Hawes. The screenplay is by Ken Nolan and Gary Spinelli based on the novel by Robert Littell. The film is produced by Hutch Parker, p.g.a., Dan Wilson, p.g.a., Rami Malek, Joel B. Michaels, with JJ Hook serving as executive producer.

Mike Tyson also known as ‚ÄúIron‚Äù Mike Tyson is a professional boxing super star, actor, producer, and writer who has dominated pop culture since his 20‚Äôs

snippet.title: Secret Level - Official Trailer | Prime Video
snippet.description:
Risk. Fight. Discover. This is what you were meant for. Enter Secret Level, the groundbreaking gaming anthology series, debuting December 10. 

Secret Level features original stories set within the worlds of some of the most beloved video games. From the creative minds behind LOVE, DEATH + ROBOTS, each of the 15 episodes is a celebration of games and gamers. Games that inspired the 15 epic stories include Armored Core, Concord, Crossfire, Dungeons & Dragons, Exodus, Honor of Kings, Mega Man, New World: Aeternum, PAC-MAN, various PlayStation Studios games, Sifu, Spelunky, The Outer Worlds, Unreal Tournament and Warhammer 40,000. Secret Level will be available exclusively on Prime Video in over 240 countries and territories worldwide starting on December 10, with additional episodic drops until December 17.

Secret Level showcases a star studded cast including Arnold Schwarzenegger (The Terminator Franchise), Kevin Hart (Jumanji), Keanu Reeves (John Wick), Temuera Morrison (The Book of Boba Fett, Chief of War), Ariana Greenblatt (Barbie), Heaven Hart, Emily Swallow (The Mandalorian), Gabriel Luna (The Last of Us, Terminator: Dark Fate), Ricky Whittle (American Gods, Land of Bad), Patrick Schwarzenegger (The White Lotus), Merle Dandridge (The Last of Us), Claudia Doumit (The Boys), Adewale Akinnuoye-Agbaje (Lost, The Union), Clive Standen (Vikings, The Morning Show), Laura Bailey (The Legend of Vox Machina), and Michael Beach (The Perfect Couple, Tulsa King).

Cannabis is finally being decriminalized in more and more places around the world. And for very good reasons! snippet.description:
Glass is one of the most important materials humans have ever made. Try out Saily by heading to https://saily.com/veritasium and remember to use coupon code veritasium to get 15% off your first purchase.

snippet.title: Watch live: SpaceX Falcon 9 rocket launches 20 Starlink satellites from Vandenberg, California
snippet.description:
Watch live coverage as SpaceX launches a Falcon 9 rocket with 20 second-generation Starlink internet satellites. Among the satellites onboard are 13 Starlink satellites that include Direct to Cell capabilities. Liftoff from pad 4E at Vandenberg Space Force Base is scheduled for Wednesday, November 13, at 9:23 p.m. PST (12:23 a.m. EST, 0523 UTC on 14th). The first-stage booster, B1082, making its 8th flight, will land on the droneship 'Of Course I Still Love You' a little more than eight minutes into the flight.

Our live coverage with commentary from Will Robinson-Smith will begin about 30 minutes before launch.

Videos like this are made possible by the support of our members. Join this channel to get access to perks:

snippet.title: Unleashing Echo Bosses Across Gielinor | Leagues V: Raging Echoes
snippet.description:
Today, we invite you to sit down and grab your notepad as @ScriticRS takes us through the grand reveal of each region's Echo Boss and their shiny new Echo Rewards!

Check out the blog for all Leagues V Teasers revealed so far: https://osrs.game/Echo-Boss-Reveal

0:00 Intro
1:45 What is an Echo Boss?
3:07 Desert
4:07 Asgarnia
5:11 Wilderness
7:08 Morytania
8:27 Fremennik
9:30 Kandarin
11:04 Tirannwn
12:19 Kourend
13:36 Varlamore
15:59 Outro

Old School RuneScape is a retro game version of RuneScape from 2007 which we returned at the community's request. The community controls the developmental direction of Old School RuneScape by voting on which updates it would like to receive.

The world's largest and most popular MMORPG, Old School RuneScape has been played by over 260 million players since the 2001 release of RuneScape. Old School RuneScape unites the intricate mechanics of modern MMOs with the nostalgic point-and-click gameplay of early role-playing games.

Old School RuneScape is free to download and play, however, the game also offers players the opportunity to purchase in-game items. Please see the PEGI information page for more information: https://pegi.info/search-pegi?q=runescape

snippet.title: Victor Wembanyama GOES OFF For New CAREER-HIGH 50 PTS!üò§| November 13, 2024
snippet.description:
Never miss a moment with the latest news, trending stories and highlights to bring you closer to your favorite players and teams.
Download now: https://link.nba.com/NBAYouTube


The San Antonio Spurs defeated the Washington Wizards, 139-130.
 
Spurs Top Performers
Victor Wembanyama ‚Äì Career-high 50 points, 6 rebounds, Career-high 8 3PM
Devin Vassell ‚Äì 17 points, 3 assists
 
Wizards Top Performers
Jordan Poole ‚Äì 42 points, 6 assists, 6 3PM
Jonas Valanƒçi≈´nas ‚Äì 16 points, 13 rebounds
 
The Spurs improve to 6-6 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 2-8.
 
Victor Wembanyama becomes the fourth youngest player in league history to record 50+ points in a game, only Brandon Jennings, LeBron James, and Devin Booker were younger.
 
Victor Wembanyama becomes the first player in Spurs franchise history to record 50+ points and 5+ 3PM in a game.
 
Victor Wembanyama becomes the 8th player in Spurs franchise history with 50+ points in a game.

snippet.title: POSSIBLE FLORIDA IMPACTS? Developing system could move into Gulf, models show | Tracking the Tropics
snippet.description:
A tropical system brewing in the Caribbean could impact Florida next week, models indicate. With the possibility of another storm impacting the hurricane-ravaged Gulf coast, WSNN Chief Meteorologist Justin Mosely joins WFLA meteorologist Amanda Holly and WFLA Now's JB Biunno to break down the models and answer viewer questions. snippet.title: How Solid State Cooling Could Change Everything
snippet.description:
How Solid State Cooling Could Change Everything. Use code 50UNDECIDED to get 50% OFF plus free shipping on your first Factor box at¬†https://bit.ly/3BRkS87! I talk about heat pumps a lot.¬†They really are the most energy efficient way to heat and cool things, but the study of caloric cooling represents the potential for a new, solid-state-esque approach to managing heat. Yup, solid state. That comes with the possibility of achieving significantly higher efficiencies without refrigerants. Caloric cooling holds massive implications for the way we cool our homes, our vehicles, and maybe even ourselves. So, how does it all work? And why does it have the potential to completely change climate control?

Some images are courtesy of Saarland University - Oliver Dietze

Watch Why The US Military Chose Silicon-Graphene Batteries https://youtu.be/l60hjFvj64s?list=PLnTSM-ORSgi7uzySCXq8VXhodHB5B5OiQ

snippet.description:
We‚Äôre turning back the clock for some classic Overwatch fun!

Return to the thrilling gameplay experience that started it all in Overwatch: Classic.

Play with the original hero roster, their classic abilities, and enjoy the chaotic fun of 6v6.

Group up with friends, old and new, as you experience the fun and camaraderie of early Overwatch.

snippet.title: The Largest Successful Heists in History
snippet.description:
In this video, we dive into some of the most audacious and successful heists in history, where thieves walked away with millions‚Äîsometimes without leaving a trace. From the infamous Great Brinks Robbery that shocked 1950s America, to the high-stakes Lufthansa Heist that inspired Hollywood, and the mystery of D. B. Cooper, who vanished without a trace after hijacking a plane and jumping mid-flight with $200,000.

We'll uncover the thrilling details behind the Great Train Robbery of 1963, where a gang managed to halt a Royal Mail train in the UK, and examine the daring British Bank of the Middle East Heist, which saw millions taken from vaults in war-torn Beirut.

Get ready for a look at the Antwerp Diamond Heist, a heist so well-planned it's known as the "heist of the century," and the unsolved case of the Isabella Stewart Gardner Museum Heist, where thieves stole priceless art worth half a billion dollars, leaving the art world mystified to this day.

0:00 7 - The Great Brink's Robbery
2:07 6 - The Lufthansa Heist
3:38 5 - The Mystery of D. B. Cooper
5:15 4 - The Great Train Robbery
6:38 3 - The British Bank of the Middle East Heist
7:37 2 - The Antwerp Diamond Heist
10:37 1 - The Isabella Stewart Gardner Museum Heist

snippet.title: Bridget Jones: Mad About the Boy | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Bridget Jones: Mad About the Boy is streaming February 13 on Peacock: https://www.peacocktv.com/stream-movies/bridget-jones-mad-about-the-boy

Two-time Academy Award¬Æ winner Ren√©e Zellweger returns to the role that established a romantic-comedy heroine for the ages, a woman whose inimitable approach to life and love redefined an entire film genre.‚ÄØ  
‚ÄØ 
Bridget Jones first blasted onto bookshelves in Helen Fielding‚Äôs literary phenomenon Bridget Jones‚Äôs Diary, which became a global bestseller and a blockbuster film. As a single career woman living in London, Bridget Jones not only introduced the world to her romantic adventures, but added ‚ÄúSingletons,‚Äù ‚ÄúSmug-Marrieds‚Äù and ‚Äúf---wittage‚Äù into the global lexicon. Bridget‚Äôs ability to triumph despite adversity led her to finally marry top lawyer Mark Darcy and to become the mother of their baby boy. Happiness at last.  
 
But in Bridget Jones: Mad About the Boy, Bridget is alone once again, widowed four years ago, when Mark (Oscar¬Æ winner Colin Firth) was killed on a humanitarian mission in the Sudan. She‚Äôs now a single mother to 9-year-old Billy and 4-year-old Mabel, and is stuck in a state of emotional limbo, raising her children with help from her loyal friends and even her former lover, Daniel Cleaver (Hugh Grant).  
‚ÄØ 
Pressured by her Urban Family ‚ÄîShazzer, Jude and Tom, her work colleague Miranda, her mother, and her gynecologist Dr. Rawlings (Oscar¬Æ winner Emma Thompson) ‚Äî to forge a new path toward life and love, Bridget goes back to work and even tries out the dating apps, where she‚Äôs soon pursued by a dreamy and enthusiastic younger man (White Lotus‚Äôs Leo Woodall). Now juggling work, home and romance, Bridget grapples with the judgment of the perfect mums at school, worries about Billy as he struggles with the absence of his father, and engages in a series of awkward interactions with her son‚Äôs rational-to-a-fault science teacher (Oscar¬Æ nominee Chiwetel Ejiofor). The returning cast includes Oscar¬Æ winner Jim Broadbent and BAFTA winner Gemma Jones as Bridget‚Äôs parents and, as a new character, Isla Fisher (Now You See Me, The Great Gatsby) as Rebecca, Bridget‚Äôs neighbor.  
 
Bridget Jones: Mad About the Boy is directed by acclaimed filmmaker Michael Morris (To Leslie, Better Call Saul), from a screenplay by BAFTA nominee Helen Fielding, based on her novel, with contributions from Emmy winner Abi Morgan (The Iron Lady, Eric) and Oscar¬Æ nominee Dan Mazer (I Give it A Year, Bridget Jones‚Äôs Baby).  
 
The film is produced for Working Title by Tim Bevan and Eric Fellner, whose films, including The Danish Girl, Darkest Hour, Fargo, Les Mis√©rables and The Theory of Everything, among others, have earned 14 Academy Awards¬Æ and six Best Picture nominations. The film is also produced by Jo Wallett (Wicked Little Letters, Catherine Called Birdy). The film is executive produced by Helen Fielding, Ren√©e Zellweger, Amelia Granger and Sarah-Jane Wright. Working Title has produced all the Bridget Jones films.  
 
Universal Pictures and StudioCanal and Miramax present a Working Title production, Bridget Jones: Mad About the Boy. The film will be released in theaters internationally by Universal Pictures and will stream exclusively on Peacock in the U.S.

snippet.title: Jeff Teague on Steph Curry & Warriors EPIC win vs. Luka Doncic, Klay Thompson & Mavs, Embiid returns
snippet.description:
On the Wednesday, November 13 episode of 520 in the Morning, Jeff Teague, DJ Wells, and B Hen react to Klay Thompson‚Äôs return to Golden State as the Mavericks faced off in the NBA Cup against Steph Curry and the Golden State Warriors. Steph turned back the clock in his EPIC performance against Luka Doncic as the Warriors came back and won 120-117. The guys also break down Joel Embiid‚Äôs return as the Philadelphia 76ers were dominated by Jalen Brunson and the New York Knicks, as well as the best stories from around the rest of the NBA.

snippet.title: Haitian gangs open fire on Spirit Airlines flight from Florida
snippet.description:
Haiti‚Äôs international airport shut down temporarily on Monday after gangs opened fire at a Spirit Airlines flight landing in Port-Au-Prince, the U.S. State Department and the airline said. The latest violence came as a new prime minister was sworn in.

The flight, headed from Fort Lauderdale to Port-Au-Prince, was hit multiple times by gunfire as it was set to land in Haiti‚Äôs capital, striking a flight attendant, who suffered minor injuries. Photos and videos obtained by The Associated Press show bullet holes dotting the interior of a plane.

The flight was diverted and landed in the Dominican Republic, according to Spirit Airlines. It appeared to be part of what the U.S. Embassy called ‚Äúgang-led efforts to block travel to and from Port-au-Prince which may include armed violence, and disruptions to roads, ports, and airports.‚Äù

MORE: https://www.wtsp.com/article/news/nation-world/haiti-gang-gunfire-hits-plane/507-9e9791e2-76b5-40dd-b178-985bc9834e78

snippet.description:
I review, breakdown and explain Yellowstone Season 5 Episode 9. I discuss the return of Season 5 Part 2 and give my reaction to the ending and the story of John Dutton's death, answer who killed him, Beth planning on getting revenge on Jamie, Kayce and Monica moving home and Rip returning from Texas where there was a lot of symbolism about change and Billy Klapper. I also give my theories and predictions for episode 10.

snippet.title: Why American Cars Are So Expensive
snippet.description:
Cars once promised independence and transportation for all Americans. Now, they are a luxury product that cost about $50,000, nearly 30% higher than just a few years ago. Affordable vehicles, especially those below the price of $20,000, have nearly disappeared. And while Automakers pulled in record profits in 2023, slim margins combined with deep investments into EV batteries, software and other technology is making it hard to produce cars much cheaper. Chinese automakers can, but they're impeded by tariffs and rules. Insiders say that is just a bandage - automakers need to compete.

Chapters:
00:56 Title card - Why American automakers can‚Äôt make cheap cars 
1:05 Chapter 1 - Affordability 
3:02 Chapter 2 - How cars got so expensive 
6:07 Chapter 3 - Making a cheaper car
9:08 Chapter 4 - Competing with China

localized.title: Why American Cars Are So Expensive
localized.description:
Cars once promised independence and transportation for all Americans. Now, they are a luxury product that cost about $50,000, nearly 30% higher than just a few years ago. Affordable vehicles, especially those below the price of $20,000, have nearly disappeared. And while Automakers pulled in record profits in 2023, slim margins combined with deep investments into EV batteries, software and other technology is making it hard to produce cars much cheaper. Chinese automakers can, but they're impeded by tariffs and rules. Insiders say that is just a bandage - automakers need to compete.
